text: Bezinghem is a commune in the Pas-de-Calais department in the Hauts-de-France region of France. ==Geography== A small village situated some 15 miles(24 km) southeast of Boulogne-sur-Mer, on the D127E road. ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Pas-de-Calais department ==References== * INSEE commune file Category:Communes of Pas-de-Calais
title: Bezinghem
